{"tid":2108980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"區諾軒宣布退出一切初選工作","createTime":"2020-07-15T02:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T02:51:41.000Z","uid":115013,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba137d13baba140723c14db88f40fa830a30f03b","tid":2108980,"uid":115013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:20:25.000Z","msg":"民主派初選落幕，特區政府、中聯辦、港澳辦接連發聲明，炮轟初選違反《基本法》和《國安法》。有份協調初選的前立法會議員區諾軒今早透過社交媒體發文，指因應兩辦發聲明指控初選，即日起退出初選一切工作。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n區諾軒在文中指，合法參與政治活動是他可付出的極限，雖然發起人一直重申初選安排合法，但執政陣營有不同理解。區諾軒指，基於現局未能確保人身安全，為身邊所有人負責，他只得退出所有初選工作。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n區諾軒形容，退出是一個沉重決定，但他會在其他崗位繼續努力，「還望各方加油、見諒。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A9%E8%BE%A6%E7%82%AE%E8%BD%9F%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95-%E5%8D%80%E8%AB%BE%E8%BB%92%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E6%98%AF%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%87%BA%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%25BD%259F%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25BB%2592%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2587%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%2599%2590%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=248e7646\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%25BD%259F%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25BB%2592%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2587%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%2